alerts-changeling-chemicals-name = Chemicals
alerts-changeling-chemicals-desc = Spend chemicals to use your abilities. Slowly regenerates.

alerts-changeling-biomass-name = Biomass
alerts-changeling-biomass-desc = Biomass affects your form stability. More biomass you have - less suspicious you look for everyone else. Absorb humanoids to recover some of it. [color=red]You won't be able to use stasis without biomass.[/color]

alerts-changeling-stasis-name = Stasis
alerts-changeling-stasis-desc = Press this to enter or leave stasis. Entry to stasis will drain all your chemicals and you'll change to dead state. You will be able to leave stasis for half of your maximum chemicals and rejuvenate after it.
